    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305860/extras/828b69218a68f21831333534c341434f.apng?t=1740357060\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305860/extras/828b69218a68f21831333534c341434f.poster.avif?t=1740357060\" class=\"bb_img\" width=483 height=63 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grooveyard is a chill puzzle game brimming with humor and skeletons. Use your magical powers to manipulate walls and guide your skeletal minions to freedom. Enjoy a mix of strategy and rhythm as you uncover the secrets of your bodiless origins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305860/extras/5728bb3a50ccc55589b1733379d9ac1b.poster.avif?t=1740357060\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305860/extras/5728bb3a50ccc55589b1733379d9ac1b.webm?t=1740357060\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305860/extras/5728bb3a50ccc55589b1733379d9ac1b.mp4?t=1740357060\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305860/extras/660fb0098c87fa5433e1ef74c513e8ca.apng?t=1740357060\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305860/extras/660fb0098c87fa5433e1ef74c513e8ca.poster.avif?t=1740357060\" class=\"bb_img\" width=483 height=105 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305860/extras/596aa73080df4f942b5b59ca4f860ec3.webp?t=1740357060\" width=18 height=22 /></span>  The demo features the complete first world of the game. The full game will have 6 worlds, each with a unique twist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305860/extras/15f682a0287ad54145344b9ce075041a.webp?t=1740357060\" width=20 height=18 /></span>  Speak with all your freed skeletons to unravel the mystery of the Grooveyard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305860/extras/cbe3156b1310baa224c0a1eba4786305.webp?t=1740357060\" width=20 height=30 /></span>  Optimize your solutions to receive higher ratings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305860/extras/4d6decf00d189b3a4c4047a23e5aa58c.webp?t=1740357060\" width=22 height=22 /></span>  Gameplay syncs with the music to create unique lofi-beats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305860/extras/5ab2ba2392a603f64085823156134f10.webp?t=1740357060\" width=20 height=20 /></span>  Fun and relaxed, perfect for a spooky challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305860/extras/7acf79c45fd7c5c3d2a87034f99033ac.apng?t=1740357060\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305860/extras/7acf79c45fd7c5c3d2a87034f99033ac.poster.avif?t=1740357060\" class=\"bb_img\" width=422 height=124 /></picture></span></p>",
